snippet.title: Space Hunter release trailer
snippet.description:
An NES Metroid inspired gameplay mod, details and download link can be found here!

https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=56702

The following maps were used for the trailer:
Vrack trilogy 
Equinox
BTSX episode 1
UACultra
